"But roll around"

2126
02:25:40,690 --> 02:25:43,730
天堂不休息
"Heaven all day"

2127
02:25:48,610 --> 02:25:53,570
我在这国家哀悼日说了什么
So, what do I say about this so- called national day of mourning?

2128
02:25:53,950 --> 02:25:57,450
我说是白种人的暴力行为
I say the white man's acts of violence should be condemned

2129
02:25:57,660 --> 02:25:59,580
该被他自己及其信念所咒骂
by our beliefs and by his own.

2130
02:25:59,790 --> 02:26:02,580
可兰经教导我们做坏事的人
The Koran teaches us that those who work evil

2131
02:26:03,040 --> 02:26:07,500
会根据他们的坏事而受到责骂和惩罚
will be condemned, punished or judged according to their works.

2132
02:26:07,710 --> 02:26:10,920
圣经说种瓜得瓜 种豆得豆
The Holy Bible teaches us that you reap what you sow.

2133
02:26:11,130 --> 02:26:12,590
这是神的裁决
This is divine justice.

2134
02:26:12,800 --> 02:26:16,640
在美国的泥土中 白种人种下了仇恨的种子
In the Americas' soil, the white man has planted seeds of hatred

2135
02:26:16,850 --> 02:26:18,720
种下了暴力的种子
the seeds of violence.

2136
02:26:18,930 --> 02:26:21,520
他准许那些种子的生长
He's allowed those weeds to grow up and choke

2137
02:26:21,730 --> 02:26:25,310
过去四百年将黑种人扼毙了
the lives of millions of black men and women for 400 years

2138
02:26:25,520 --> 02:26:28,820
印度人过去五百年的生活
and the lives of Indians in these Americas for 500 years.

2139
02:26:29,030 --> 02:26:34,240
现在同样的种子令花农窒息 他是主要的花农
And now those same weeds have choked one of his own gardeners, his chief gardener.

2140
02:26:34,450 --> 02:26:37,700
你问我说的话 我所说的是圣经所说的
You ask me what I say. I only say what the Bible says.

2141
02:26:37,950 --> 02:26:40,200
我所说的是可兰经所说的
I say what the Koran says.

2142
02:26:40,950 --> 02:26:42,660
我说那是正义
I say it's justice.

2143
02:26:47,540 --> 02:26:50,090
你不觉得懊悔吗?
Don't you even feel a bit of remorse

2144
02:26:50,250 --> 02:26:52,800
肯尼迪总统被行刺后
saddened by President Kennedy's assassination?

2145
02:26:52,970 --> 02:26:56,260
我不认为有人会否认
I don't think anyone would deny that when you send chickens

2146
02:26:56,470 --> 02:26:58,260
当你在早上放出你的小鸡
out from your barnyard

2147
02:26:58,470 --> 02:27:02,020
它们便会在晚上回到你身边 而不会去到的邻居那边
those chickens will return to your barnyard, not your neighbor's.

2148
02:27:02,230 --> 02:27:05,560
我认为这是魔鬼的 小鸡总会回到枝头的家中
It's an example of the devil's chickens coming home to roost.

2149
02:27:05,730 --> 02:27:08,770
他派出去的小鸡在 这里及外地所犯的暴力
The violence that he's perpetrated here and abroad

2150
02:27:08,980 --> 02:27:12,900
便是在伯明罕的四个孩子
be it four children in Birmingham, or Medgar Evers, or in Africa

2151
02:27:13,110 --> 02:27:15,610
同样的暴力己招致应得的报应
this same violence has claimed one of their own.

2152
02:27:15,820 --> 02:27:19,740
作为一个年老的农人 小鸡的回巢不会令我感忧愁
Being a farm boy, chickens coming home to roost never made me sad.

2153
02:27:19,910 --> 02:27:21,540
那只会令我高兴
In fact, it's only made me glad.

2154
02:27:31,210 --> 02:27:32,500
你
Did you

2155
02:27:33,510 --> 02:27:36,010
有看今天的报纸吗
read the paper today?

2156
02:27:38,760 --> 02:27:40,430
有
Yes, sir. I did.

2157
02:27:43,720 --> 02:27:48,650
那就是你做的陈述
That was a bad statement you made.

2158
02:27:50,770 --> 02:27:54,440
你知道我的指示
You knew from my instructions

2159
02:27:54,690 --> 02:27:59,610
没有一个牧师可以反抗这人
no minister was to make any statements against this man.

2160
02:27:59,820 --> 02:28:02,370
国家爱这个人
The country loved this man.

2161
02:28:02,700 --> 02:28:04,540
你已经
You have made it

2162
02:28:04,950 --> 02:28:06,120
令
hard

2163
02:28:06,960 --> 02:28:08,620
伊斯兰教徒很难受
for Muslims

2164
02:28:09,000 --> 02:28:10,880
总括来说
in general.

2165
02:28:13,420 --> 02:28:14,500
是的
Yes, sir.

2166
02:28:14,710 --> 02:28:19,510
我们不可惹上
We must disassociate ourselves

2167
02:28:19,720 --> 02:28:22,010
对头人
from your terrible blunder.

2168
02:28:24,560 --> 02:28:26,560
我要静化你
I must silence you.

2169
02:28:27,140 --> 02:28:29,060
九十天
For 90 days

2170
02:28:30,310 --> 02:28:36,320
你肯定不可以向外发表言论
you must not make any statements to the press

2171
02:28:37,070 --> 02:28:41,410
或在任何教堂中作演说
nor are you to speak at any temples.

2172
02:28:42,740 --> 02:28:43,910
知道
Yes, sir.

2173
02:28:45,490 --> 02:28:48,410
我百份百服从
Yes, sir. I submit 100 percent.

2174
02:29:46,890 --> 02:29:47,970
让我们静静
Leave us alone.

2175
02:29:49,060 --> 02:29:51,270
- 贝蒂? - 让我们静静 别再打电话来
- Betty? - Leave us alone. Stop calling here.

2176
02:29:51,480 --> 02:29:54,900
谁主使你来? 我们在这里有孩子
Who's putting you up to this? We have children here!

2177
02:29:55,230 --> 02:29:56,650
停止!
Stop it!

2178
02:30:09,410 --> 02:30:10,750
没事了
It's all right.

2179
02:30:11,250 --> 02:30:12,910
他们不断打来
They keep calling.

2180
02:30:14,080 --> 02:30:15,920
他们总是打
They keep calling.

2181
02:30:18,500 --> 02:30:19,800
叫
Just

2182
02:30:21,510 --> 02:30:23,590
他们睡吧
take the babies and put them to bed.

2183
02:30:24,260 --> 02:30:26,590
来 我们现在上床了
Come on, babies. Let's go to bed now.

2184
02:30:27,100 --> 02:30:28,760
- 睡觉时间了 - 来吧
- Bedtime. - Come on.

2185
02:30:29,430 --> 02:30:30,770
来吧
Let's go.

2186
02:30:32,100 --> 02:30:35,690
- 晚安 妈妈 - 晚安 爸爸
- Good night, Mommy. - Good night, Daddy.

2187
02:30:35,860 --> 02:30:38,230
- 晚安 西德尼 - 晚安
- Good night, Sidney. - Night- night.

2188
02:30:50,950 --> 02:30:53,620
牧师兄弟 我要坦白对你说
Brother Minister, I have to level with you.

2189
02:30:54,460 --> 02:30:56,460
他们给了我任务
They gave me a mission

2190
02:30:56,880 --> 02:30:58,290
但我做不到
but I couldn't do it.

2191
02:30:59,340 --> 02:31:01,920
- 我爱你 - 什么任务
- I love you all. - What kind of mission?

2192
02:31:04,720 --> 02:31:06,680
弄你的车
To wire your car

2193
02:31:06,890 --> 02:31:09,220
使你开车时
so it would explode

2194
02:31:09,640 --> 02:31:11,930
便爆炸
when you turned the ignition.

2195
02:31:13,230 --> 02:31:17,230
牧师说你在散布穆罕默德的假消息
The ministers say you're spreading untruths about Mr. Muhammad.

2196
02:31:17,650 --> 02:31:20,520
他们说你是最大的骗子
They say that you're the greatest hypocrite

2197
02:31:20,730 --> 02:31:22,230
犹大
a Judas

2198
02:31:22,650 --> 02:31:24,570
一个大骗子
a Benedict Arnold.

2199
02:31:25,990 --> 02:31:29,570
牧师说你的舌头该被割下来
The ministers say that your tongue should be cut out

2200
02:31:30,080 --> 02:31:33,330
送到穆罕默德先生门前
and delivered to Mr. Muhammad's doorstep.

2201
02:31:34,040 --> 02:31:35,790
你认为呢?
And what do you say?

2202
02:31:36,000 --> 02:31:37,710
我支持你 牧师兄弟
I'm with you, Brother Minister.

2203
02:31:37,920 --> 02:31:39,380
你会没命的 是的
You'll be marked for death.

2204
02:31:40,000 --> 02:31:41,170
是的
Yes, sir.

2205
02:31:42,250 --> 02:31:44,210
就让我死吧
Let me die then.

2206
02:31:56,770 --> 02:31:58,980
我不能介于你和你父亲之间
I can't come between you and your father.

2207
02:31:59,440 --> 02:32:01,690
- 你是我父亲 - 回家
- You're my father. - Go on home.

2208
02:32:03,780 --> 02:32:05,940
不要回来 这是命令
Don't come back. That's an order.

2209
02:32:13,540 --> 02:32:15,160
是的
Yes, sir.

2210
02:32:27,630 --> 02:32:31,470
因为一九六四年被 预定为种族问题的爆发年
Because 1964 threatens to be an explosive year on the racial front

2211
02:32:31,680 --> 02:32:36,310
我召开这记者会来澄清我立场
I have called this press conference to clarify my position in that struggle.

2212
02:32:36,600 --> 02:32:40,560
伊斯兰国家的内乱迫了我出来
Internal differences within the Nation of Islam have forced me out of it.

2213
02:32:40,730 --> 02:32:44,770
在过去 我提倡穆罕默德的言论
In the past, I thought and spoke the words of the Honorable Elijah Muhammad.

2214
02:32:44,980 --> 02:32:46,900
我说了所有一切
Everything I said, I started with:

2215
02:32:47,070 --> 02:32:50,410
由穆罕默德教导我们开始
"The Honorable Elijah Muhammad teaches us" thus- and- so.

2216
02:32:50,660 --> 02:32:52,280
那些日子己结束了
That day is over.

2217
02:32:52,490 --> 02:32:56,200
从现在起 我为自己说话 以自己的想法去思考
From now on I speak my own words, and I think my own thoughts.

2218
02:32:56,410 --> 02:32:59,120
现在我可以更自主和自由
Now that I have more, uh, independence of action

2219
02:32:59,330 --> 02:33:02,750
我会用更好的方法 和其他人
I'll use a more flexible approach in working with others

2220
02:33:02,920 --> 02:33:04,590
合力解决这问题
to solve this problem.

2221
02:33:04,750 --> 02:33:07,090
我不和其他黑人领袖争吵
I'm not out to fight other Negro leaders.

2222
02:33:07,260 --> 02:33:10,760
我忘了其他黑人领袖说过有关我的坏话
I've forgotten every bad thing other leaders said about me

2223
02:33:10,930 --> 02:33:14,760
我祈求他们也要忘记我所说有关他的坏话
and I pray they'll forget the many bad things I said about them.

2224
02:33:14,930 --> 02:33:19,020
我们一定要一同工作来找出问题的答案
We must work together to find a common solution to a common problem.

2225
02:33:19,560 --> 02:33:22,440
我会在纽约组织新的伊斯兰教教堂
I will organize and lead a new mosque in New York City:

2226
02:33:22,650 --> 02:33:24,360
叫伊斯兰教徒的教堂
Muslim Mosque, Incorporated.

2227
02:33:24,770 --> 02:33:28,280
这会给我们宗教基础 及所需的精神力量
This gives us the religious base and the spiritual, uh, force

2228
02:33:28,490 --> 02:33:31,110
来使我们的人脱离那些
necessary to rid our people of the vices

2229
02:33:31,360 --> 02:33:33,700
毁坏我们社会道德的邪恶
that destroy the moral fiber of our community.

2230
02:33:33,910 --> 02:33:36,280
我们的政治哲学会是黑种人国教
Our politics will be Black Nationalism

2231
02:33:36,450 --> 02:33:39,540
意思是我们要控制社会的政治
meaning, we want to control our community's politics.

2232
02:33:39,750 --> 02:33:42,170
伊斯兰教徒的教堂
The Muslim Mosque, Inc. Will remain open

2233
02:33:42,370 --> 02:33:45,630
会接受各区的意见和经济支助
for ideas and financial aid from all quarters.

2234
02:33:46,210 --> 02:33:49,130
白种人可帮助我们 但不能加入
Whites can help us, but they can't join us.

2235
02:33:49,380 --> 02:33:52,840
没有黑白联盟 直到有首个黑人联盟出现
There can't be black- white unity until there's first black unity.

2236
02:33:53,140 --> 02:33:54,760
我们不能联合其他人
We can't unite with others

2237
02:33:54,970 --> 02:33:57,850
直到我们团结自己
until we've first learned to unite amongst ourselves.

2238
02:33:58,060 --> 02:34:00,180
要让人们接受我们
We can't be acceptable to others

2239
02:34:00,390 --> 02:34:03,140
先要接受自己
until we have first proven acceptable to ourselves.

2240
02:34:03,310 --> 02:34:06,810
要完全明白伊斯兰教
In my desire to fully understand the religion of Islam

2241
02:34:07,020 --> 02:34:11,150
像其他七亿五千万的伊斯兰教徒
as practiced by 750 million Muslims around the world

2242
02:34:11,320 --> 02:34:15,740
我要朝圣 或神圣旅程 去麦加朝圣
I intend to make a pilgrimage, or holy, uh, journey, to Mecca.

2243
02:34:15,950 --> 02:34:18,700
这是每个伊斯兰教徒的责任
This pilgrimage is a religious requirement

2244
02:34:18,910 --> 02:34:21,500
使得他们在一生中
or duty, of every Muslim that is able

2245
02:34:21,660 --> 02:34:25,460
最少朝圣一次
uh, to make the pilgrimage at least once in his lifetime.

2246
02:34:39,390 --> 02:34:41,020
我是埃及人 你是谁
I'm Egyptian. And you?

2247
02:34:41,310 --> 02:34:42,390
美国人
American.

2248
02:34:42,600 --> 02:34:43,690
你叫什么名
What's your name?

2249
02:34:43,850 --> 02:34:46,190
- 马尔克姆 - 马尔克姆
- Malcolm. - Malcolm.

2250
02:34:56,660 --> 02:34:58,950
好的 我过去拿
Yes, I want to get

2251
02:35:00,490 --> 02:35:02,620
多少钱? 二十埃及磅
- How much? - Twenty Egyptian pounds.

2252
02:35:03,370 --> 02:35:04,620
一个?
For one?

2253
02:35:04,830 --> 02:35:07,210
- 特价给你 - 特价给我
- Special price for you. - Special for me!

2254
02:35:07,380 --> 02:35:10,800
谢谢 我在哪里可找到更好的
Okay, thank you. Where can I get a better price?

2255
02:35:16,260 --> 02:35:18,180
- 你叫什么名 - 穆罕默德
- What's your name? - Mohammed.

2256
02:35:18,390 --> 02:35:19,930
马尔克姆 我是马尔克姆
Mohammed, I'm Malcolm.

2257
02:35:21,060 --> 02:35:23,560
- 马尔克姆 你呢 - 加玛
- Malcolm X. And you? - Gamaal.

2258
02:35:23,810 --> 02:35:27,810
好了 我从美国哈林来
All right, Gamaal. I'm from, uh, Harlem. From the United States.

2259
02:35:27,980 --> 02:35:29,020
哈里?
Harem?

2260
02:35:29,190 --> 02:35:30,230
- 哈林 - 哈里
- Harlem. - Hareem?

2261
02:35:30,400 --> 02:35:32,570
不是哈里 是哈林
No, not Hareem. Harlem.

2262
02:35:32,740 --> 02:35:34,610
你可带我周围看看吗
Can you show me around?

2263
02:35:34,820 --> 02:35:36,610
不要 印度大麻
No. No hashish.

2264
02:35:39,330 --> 02:35:41,580
金字塔!
You know, the pyramids.

2265
02:35:41,740 --> 02:35:43,490
不 金字塔 金字塔 金字塔
No, pyramids. Pyramids. Pyramids.

2266
02:35:48,210 --> 02:35:49,920
- 金字塔? - 金字塔
- Pyramids? - Pyramids.

2267
02:35:50,090 --> 02:35:52,380
- 你可以带我去吗? - 可以
- You're gonna take me? - Yes. Yes.

2268
02:35:52,760 --> 02:35:54,960
狮身人面像
Sphinx. Sphinx.

2269
02:37:16,420 --> 02:37:18,170
我的爱人 贝蒂
My darling Betty:

2270
02:37:18,670 --> 02:37:22,680
我去到哪里都受到欢迎
Everywhere I go, I am welcomed as a representative of our people.

2271
02:37:23,010 --> 02:37:26,180
我们的争斗为人所知和敬重
Our struggle is known and respected worldwide.

2272
02:37:26,680 --> 02:37:30,480
有两个白种人秘密地跟着我
Coincidentally, two white men follow me around wherever I go.

2273
02:37:30,850 --> 02:37:32,770
我不知他们是替谁工作的
I wonder who they're working for?

2274
02:37:33,270 --> 02:37:35,730
如果我是赌徒 我会说是中央情报告
If I was a betting man, I'd say the CIA.

2275
02:37:35,940 --> 02:37:37,110
你认为呢
What's your guess?

2276
02:37:38,110 --> 02:37:40,150
那天我要到阿拉伯
Today I arrived in Arabia.

2277
02:37:40,780 --> 02:37:44,700
我从未如此被款待过
I have never witnessed such sincere hospitality

2278
02:37:44,870 --> 02:37:46,990
真正的兄弟
and true brotherhood

2279
02:37:47,200 --> 02:37:48,830
在这训练的时候
as practiced here

2280
02:37:49,040 --> 02:37:52,290
在亚伯拉罕的古代家中
in the ancient home of Abraham, Mohammed

2281
02:37:52,830 --> 02:37:56,040
穆罕默德及圣经的伟大先知
and the great prophets of the Scriptures."

2282
02:38:02,300 --> 02:38:04,890
今天在无数人面前
Today, with thousands of others

2283
02:38:05,050 --> 02:38:08,640
我在麦加宣告神的伟大
I proclaimed God's greatness in the sacred city of Mecca.

2284
02:38:09,730 --> 02:38:13,140
穿着朝圣服 我在卡巴附近绕七个圈
In the ihram garb, I made my seven circuits around the Kaaba.

2285
02:38:13,730 --> 02:38:16,060
我喝沙井的水
I drank from the well of Zem Zem.

2286
02:38:16,480 --> 02:38:19,230
我在亚法山上向真主祈祷
I prayed to Allah from Mount Arafat.

2287
02:38:19,570 --> 02:38:23,450
那是我生命中唯一一次 站在全能的创造者前
It was the only time in my life that I stood before the creator of all

2288
02:38:23,660 --> 02:38:26,160
感到像个完全的人
and felt like a complete human being.

2289
02:38:46,350 --> 02:38:48,930
你可能被这些言词吓到
Now, you may be shocked by these words

2290
02:38:49,100 --> 02:38:52,980
但我吃同一碟食物 喝同一杯水
but I've eaten from the same plate, drunk from the same glass

2291
02:38:53,190 --> 02:38:57,190
向同一个神祈祷 和那些蓝眼睛金发
and prayed to the same God with Muslims whose eyes were blue

2292
02:38:57,400 --> 02:39:01,650
白皮肤的伊斯兰教徒一起
whose hair was blond, and whose skin was the whitest of white.

2293
02:39:01,860 --> 02:39:03,610
我们全是兄弟
And we were all brothers

2294
02:39:03,780 --> 02:39:04,820
真的
truly.

2295
02:39:05,030 --> 02:39:09,620
不同肤色及种族的人 全相信同一个神和人道
People of all colors and races believing in one God, in one humanity.

2296
02:39:24,300 --> 02:39:26,510
在这圣地的每一刻
Each hour in this sacred land gives me

2297
02:39:26,720 --> 02:39:30,300
使我对美国有更深的见解
greater spiritual insight into what is happening in America.

2298
02:39:30,720 --> 02:39:35,020
不能怪美国的黑种人
The American Negro can never be blamed for his racial animosities.

