我说 我们打算在这里听他们演奏蓝调
"I said, we're going down here Listen to them play them blues"

2490
02:54:15,480 --> 02:54:17,360
- 喂 - 起来 兄弟
- Hello. - Wake up, brother.

2491
02:54:17,900 --> 02:54:19,780
以真主的名义
As- Salaam- Alaikum.

2492
02:54:28,040 --> 02:54:31,460
你听着 如果没接近我家
You hear me and hear me well. You come anywhere near my family

2493
