我在一间酒店
I'm in a hotel.

2505
02:55:09,080 --> 02:55:10,080
在一间酒店
In a hotel.

2506
02:55:10,450 --> 02:55:13,120
- 女儿睡了吗 - 睡着了
- The girls asleep? - Yes.

2507
02:55:13,290 --> 02:55:16,420
我刚放她们上床
I just put them down to bed.

2508
02:55:17,290 --> 02:55:19,460
我们明天可以见面吗
Can we come to the meeting tomorrow?

2509
02:55:21,760 --> 02:55:23,420
不可以
No, I don't think so.

2510
02:55:24,430 --> 02:55:27,260
我和女孩也想见你 我们怀念你
The girls and I want to see you. We miss you.

2511
02:55:28,140 --> 02:55:30,140
贝蒂 那太危险了
Betty, it's too dangerous.

2512
02:55:30,930 --> 02:55:33,060
已经很危险了
It's been dangerous.

2513
02:55:36,230 --> 02:55:39,270
听着 我从未向任何人说过这
Listen, I haven't told this to anybody

2514
02:55:41,980 --> 02:55:43,780
但我一直在想
but I've been thinking

2515
02:55:43,990 --> 02:55:47,320
我们近日遇到的事
about what's been happening to me lately, to us lately

2516
02:55:48,160 --> 02:55:51,580
我不会再说伊斯兰教国家在我的背后
and I'm gonna stop saying The Nation of Islam's behind this.

2517
02:55:51,790 --> 02:55:55,160
我知道他们能不能做到 我训练他们
I know what they can and can't do. I trained them.

2518
02:55:57,000 --> 02:56:00,130
近日发生的事
Some of the things that have been happening lately.

2519
02:56:02,170 --> 02:56:05,420
我不会再那样说
I'm gonna stop saying it's just The Nation of Islam.

2520
02:56:05,630 --> 02:56:07,680
他们不是单独工作
They're not working alone.

2521
02:56:08,300 --> 02:56:10,140
他们找到很多帮手
They're getting a lot of help.

2522
02:56:10,350 --> 02:56:12,140
你肯定?
Are you sure?

2523
02:56:13,020 --> 02:56:14,470
我想念你 贝蒂
I miss you, Betty.

2524
02:56:18,100 --> 02:56:20,480
就算你走了 你也会和我们一起
You're with us even when you're away.

2525
02:56:20,690 --> 02:56:24,030
听着 你明天去亚多巴
Now, listen, you come on down to the Audubon tomorrow.

2526
02:56:24,990 --> 02:56:28,780
不会有事的 此事不会令我们失望
We'll be all right. We're not gonna let this get us down. We'll be fine.

2527
02:56:28,990 --> 02:56:31,120
你和女儿一同下来
You come on down. Bring the girls too.

2528
02:56:31,330 --> 02:56:33,910
女儿和我非常挂念你
The girls and I miss you so much.

2529
02:56:34,080 --> 02:56:35,290
明天见
I'll see you tomorrow.

2530
02:56:35,500 --> 02:56:37,580
和一个皇帝比较 这是个僧侣
Compared to King, this guy's a monk.

2531
02:56:37,790 --> 02:56:40,830
- 晚安 睡个好觉 我爱你 - 晚安
- Good night. Sleep well. I love you. - Good night.

2532
02:56:53,850 --> 02:56:56,520
甜心 坐好
Sweetheart, Attallah, sit back.

2533
02:56:56,730 --> 02:56:59,940
坐直些
Sit up. Sit up straight.

2534
02:57:26,090 --> 02:57:27,880
我想要那洋娃娃
Mama, I want the doll.

2535
02:58:01,580 --> 02:58:02,920
坐下
Go sit down.

2536
02:58:14,390 --> 02:58:15,430
小姐妹?
Sister?

2537
02:58:19,140 --> 02:58:22,100
- 要对那个好人说什么? - 谢谢
- What do you say to the nice man? - Thank you.

2538
02:58:22,270 --> 02:58:24,440
别客气 小姐妹
You're very welcome, my beautiful sister.

2539
02:58:25,560 --> 02:58:26,610
拜拜
Bye- bye.

2540
02:58:43,000 --> 02:58:45,290
牧师还未到
The minister hasn't arrived yet.

2541
02:58:45,630 --> 02:58:48,130
放心 他会像时钟般准时
Don't worry. He'll be here like clockwork.

2542
