Are you okay?

2546
02:59:30,300 --> 02:59:33,300
- 没有事 - 我认得你
- Yeah. - Good. I recognize you.

2547
02:59:33,510 --> 02:59:36,010
别理那些人
Don't you pay them folks no never mind.

2548
02:59:36,220 --> 02:59:38,850
你只是做你所做的事
You just keep right on doing what you doing.

2549
02:59:40,930 --> 02:59:42,100
是 太太
Yes, ma'am.

2550
02:59:42,270 --> 02:59:45,020
- 我会为你祈祷 儿子 - 谢谢
- I'll pray for you, son. - Well, thank you.

2551
02:59:45,390 --> 02:59:47,270
主会保护你
Jesus will protect you.

2552
03:00:01,700 --> 03:00:03,200
约章准备好了吗
Is the charter ready?

2553
03:00:03,370 --> 03:00:05,500
- 没有 - 牧师兄弟
- no, Brother Minister. - No?

2554
03:00:07,080 --> 03:00:08,540
没有 为什么?
No? Why not?

2555
03:00:10,920 --> 03:00:12,840
你有足够时间 不是吗
You had enough time, didn't you?

2556
03:00:13,050 --> 03:00:15,340
我道歉 我们会在下星期有
I apologize. We'll have it next week.

2557
03:00:15,550 --> 03:00:17,840
不是下星期要 是今天要
We don't have next week. We need it today.

2558
03:00:18,050 --> 03:00:20,390
他们等着今天听
The people want to hear the charter today.

2559
03:00:20,600 --> 03:00:22,260
下星期 牧师
Next week, Minister.

2560
03:00:28,730 --> 03:00:30,100
神父到了吗
Is the reverend here?

2561
03:00:30,440 --> 03:00:33,730
神父说他不能来
The reverend called and said he wouldn't be able to attend.

2562
03:00:35,240 --> 03:00:38,740
所以我们没有开场讲者 没有约章
So now we don't have an opening speaker or a charter.

2563
03:00:39,530 --> 03:00:42,370
我的意思是 为何昨晚不告诉我
Why didn't you say this last night when I talked to you?

2564
03:00:42,580 --> 03:00:45,410
- 我找过贝蒂姐妹 - 你不必叫她
- I called Sister Betty - You didn't have to call her.

2565
03:00:45,620 --> 03:00:47,580
你该告诉我 找她干什么
You should've told me. Why tell her?

2566
03:00:47,790 --> 03:00:50,080
- 我以为 - 别以为
- I assumed that - Don't assume anything!

2567
03:01:00,590 --> 03:01:01,760
下去
Go on down front.

2568
03:01:02,100 --> 03:01:04,640
- 姐妹 你也是 - 是
- Sister, you go on with the brother. - Yes, sir.

2569
03:01:19,410 --> 03:01:20,660
马尔克姆
Malcolm.

2570
03:01:23,280 --> 03:01:24,490
有什么不妥
What's wrong?

2571
03:01:29,000 --> 03:01:31,330
现在是时间做瑞德士了
It's a time for martyrs now.

2572
03:01:35,050 --> 03:01:36,920
我感到
The way I feel

2573
