不该今天出去那里
I shouldn't go out there today.

2574
03:01:42,010 --> 03:01:44,510
好 我们取消它
Fine. Let's cancel it.

2575
03:01:47,520 --> 03:01:49,680
我妻子和我的孩子在外面吗?
My wife out there? My children?

2576
03:01:50,100 --> 03:01:52,100
正如往常般下去
Down front, as always.

2577
03:01:55,110 --> 03:01:57,780
你出去外面的电话亭
Go out to the pay phone outside.

2578
03:01:59,280 --> 03:02:03,570
找神父看他可否去那里
Call up the reverend, see if he can make it down here.

2579
03:02:03,780 --> 03:02:07,950
我要去看守 我该在那里保护你
I gotta be on post, Malcolm. I'm supposed to be out there guarding you.

2580
03:02:08,160 --> 03:02:13,080
- 况且 那是秘书的工作 - 去打电话
- Besides, that's a duty for secretaries - Go out to the pay phone.

2581
03:02:13,630 --> 03:02:15,210
给神父问
Call up the reverend.

2582
03:02:15,710 --> 03:02:17,550
他可否下去
See if he can make it down here.

2583
03:02:22,010 --> 03:02:23,220
好
Fine.

2584
03:03:12,180 --> 03:03:15,440
请大家做好 节目开始
Please, let's settle down. Let's get the program started.

2585
03:03:18,570 --> 03:03:19,860
谢谢
Thank you.

2586
03:03:24,660 --> 03:03:27,490
我为刚才的事道歉
I apologize for raising my voice earlier.

2587
03:03:27,700 --> 03:03:29,280
十分不敬
It was very disrespectful.

2588
03:03:29,540 --> 03:03:32,040
牧师兄弟 我明白的
Brother Minister, I understand.

2589
03:03:41,050 --> 03:03:42,340
生活方式在变
Why, styles are changing

2590
03:03:42,510 --> 03:03:45,430
思想在变 所以一切都在变
minds are changing, why, everything is changing.

2591
03:03:46,090 --> 03:03:50,140
你和我要留意我们转变得很快的生活
So you and I must consider that we're living in very changing times.

2592
03:03:50,560 --> 03:03:54,020
今天真的事 明天或许便不是真的了
And what might be true today may not be true tomorrow.

2593
03:03:54,940 --> 03:03:57,600
没有进一步的烦扰 不用多作介绍
And without any further ado, I present to you

2594
03:03:58,060 --> 03:04:00,770
马尔克姆牧师兄弟 我会祈祷
Brother Minister Malcolm. And I pray

2595
03:04:01,230 --> 03:04:04,940
你和我会留心听
that you and I will listen. Listen

2596
03:04:05,570 --> 03:04:09,120
留心听便会明白 谢谢
hear and understand. Thank you.

2597
03:04:16,120 --> 03:04:17,460
爸爸!
Daddy!

2598
03:04:31,810 --> 03:04:33,970
放开你的手!
Get your hand out of my pocket!

2599
03:04:35,680 --> 03:04:36,810
兄弟
Brother.

2600
03:04:36,980 --> 03:04:38,100
兄弟 请等等
Please. Hold it.

2601
03:04:39,770 --> 03:04:41,810
冷静下来 天!
Calm down. Please, brothers!

2602
03:04:43,480 --> 03:04:44,780
天啊 马尔克姆!
Malcolm!

2603
03:04:46,400 --> 03:04:47,650
马尔克姆!
Malcolm!

2604
03:05:20,520 --> 03:05:21,850
马尔克姆!
Malcolm!

2605
03:05:24,650 --> 03:05:26,730
叫救护车!
Get an ambulance!

2606
03:05:26,940 --> 03:05:29,360
- 叫救护车! - 是他们杀死他!
- Somebody get an ambulance! - They killed him!

2607
03:05:31,160 --> 03:05:33,160
是他们杀死他!
They killed him!

2608
03:05:41,880 --> 03:05:45,130
我要杀了你! 我要杀了你!
I'm gonna kill you! I'm gonna kill you!

2609
03:05:48,050 --> 03:05:49,590
抓住他
Get him!

2610
03:05:51,010 --> 03:05:53,220
他杀了他!
He killed Malcolm!

2611
03:06:03,900 --> 03:06:05,860
退开!
Back off, people!

2612
03:06:40,140 --> 03:06:42,770
我们这里有人身中多抢
We've got multiple shooting victims.

2613
03:06:52,150 --> 03:06:53,450
别挡着路
Get out of the way!

2614
03:06:58,700 --> 03:06:59,740
走开
Move!

2615
03:07:08,090 --> 03:07:11,050
退后 离开这里 走开
Stand back! Get out of the way! Get back!

2616
03:07:12,930 --> 03:07:15,380
请给我一个陈词!
Give us a statement, sir! Please!

2617
03:07:15,590 --> 03:07:19,010
你所认识的马尔克姆埃克斯不在了
The person you know as Malcolm X is no more.

2618
03:07:19,350 --> 03:07:21,350
马尔克姆埃克斯被杀
The assassination

2619
03:07:21,600 --> 03:07:25,190
是件不幸的悲剧
of Malcolm X was an unfortunate tragedy.

2620
03:07:25,600 --> 03:07:28,270
那反映我们的国家中
And it reveals that there are still

2621
03:07:28,610 --> 03:07:31,690
仍有很多人
uh, numerous people in our nation who have

2622
03:07:31,940 --> 03:07:36,610
以为可通过谋杀来表达不满
degenerated to the point of expressing dissent through murder

2623
03:07:36,870 --> 03:07:41,410
我们没有学到 怎样和平表达不满
and we haven't learned to disagree without being violently disagreeable.

2624
03:07:42,700 --> 03:07:43,790
在这里
Here

2625
03:07:44,540 --> 03:07:47,210
在这最后的时刻
at this final hour

2626
03:07:47,790 --> 03:07:50,040
在这清静的地方
in this quiet place

2627
03:07:50,750 --> 03:07:53,050
哈林要告别
Harlem has come to bid farewell

2628
03:07:53,260 --> 03:07:55,680
最光亮的希望
to one of its brightest hopes

2629
03:07:56,680 --> 03:07:58,680
现在光辉地
extinguished now

2630
03:07:59,140 --> 03:08:01,810
永远离开我们
and gone from us forever.

2631
03:08:02,680 --> 03:08:05,730
在我们记忆深处
It is not in the memory of man that this

2632
03:08:05,940 --> 03:08:07,520
再没有其他人
beleaguered, unfortunate

2633
03:08:07,690 --> 03:08:09,860
比这位勇敢的青年人
but nonetheless proud community

2634
03:08:10,230 --> 03:08:14,650
更勇敢更冒险了
has found a braver, more gallant young champion

2635
03:08:14,900 --> 03:08:18,360
一个仍未被征服的
than this Afro- American who lies before us

2636
03:08:19,320 --> 03:08:21,330
非洲美国人
unconquered still.

2637
03:08:23,200 --> 03:08:25,580
我再说一次因为他想我
I say the word again as he would want me to:

2638
03:08:25,790 --> 03:08:27,160
非洲美国人
Afro- American.

2639
03:08:27,370 --> 03:08:30,710
非洲美国人马尔克姆
Afro- American Malcolm.

2640
03:08:30,880 --> 03:08:33,630
马尔克姆一早己不是黑奴
Malcolm had stopped being "Negro"

2641
03:08:33,840 --> 03:08:35,170
早已不是了
years ago.

2642
03:08:35,380 --> 03:08:40,340
那实在太弱少了 对他来说太弱了
It had become too small, too puny, too weak a word for him.

2643
03:08:40,680 --> 03:08:42,890
马尔克姆比那更大
Malcolm was bigger than that.

2644
03:08:43,180 --> 03:08:44,470
马尔克姆己变成
Malcolm had become

2645
03:08:44,730 --> 03:08:46,930
非洲美国人了
an Afro- American.

2646
03:08:47,230 --> 03:08:49,440
他绝望地想要使
And he wanted so desperately

2647
03:08:49,980 --> 03:08:52,570
我们所有人
that we, that all his people

2648
03:08:52,770 --> 03:08:55,900
也成为非洲美国人
would become Afro- Americans too.

2649
03:08:59,910 --> 03:09:03,370
仍有人认为要
There are those who still consider it their duty

2650
03:09:03,580 --> 03:09:07,250
作为黑种人朋友一样
as friends of the Negro people, to tell us

2651
03:09:07,790 --> 03:09:09,540
告诉我们来咒骂他
to revile him.

2652
03:09:09,750 --> 03:09:13,040
令他们不存在我们的记忆里
